sources.style.sass:
html
	scroll-behavior: smooth
body
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-weight: normal
	margin: 0
	color: #000
html,	body
	height: 100%
*
	box-sizing: border-box
	margin: 0
	padding: 0

.container
	max-width: 1280px
	width: 100%
	margin: 0 auto
	padding: 0 15px

.wrapper
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	min-height: 100%
	overflow: hidden
.main-page
	flex: 1 0 auto
.footer
	flex: 0 0 auto

.slider-button-prev,
.slider-button-next
	position: absolute
	top: 50%
	z-index: 10
	transform: translateY(-50%)
	color: #009DFF
	width: 52px
	height: 52px
	border: 1px solid
	border-radius: 50%
	transition: opacity 0.5s
	opacity: 0.5
	cursor: pointer
	display: flex
	align-items: center
	justify-content: center
	&:hover
		opacity: 1
	
.logo
	max-width: 310px
	width: 100%
	display: flex
	align-items: center
	svg
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			width: 50px
			height: 50px
			
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
		max-width: 200px
	&__wrapper
		margin-left: 15px
	&__title
		font-size: 30px
		font-weight: 900
		color: #005387
		margin: 0
		letter-spacing: 0.11em
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
			font-size: 24px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			font-size: 18px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			font-size: 14px
			letter-spacing: 0.165em
		&_green
			color: #05CD99
	&__subtitle
		font-size: 12px
		margin: 0
		color: #190A3E
		font-weight: normal
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			font-size: 8px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			font-size: 6px

/** btns **/
.btn
	width: 100%
	height: 70px
	display: flex
	font-size: 14px
	border-radius: 55px
	border: 0
	align-items: center
	justify-content: center
	max-width: 240px
	text-decoration: none
	color: #000
	font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif
	transition: all .2s
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
		max-width: 200px
		height: 50px
	&:hover
		cursor: pointer
	&_type-1
		max-width: 175px
		height: 30px
		font-size: 12px
		border: 1px solid #000
	&_type-main
		box-shadow: 8px 8px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #24FAED 0%, #00C58A 100%)
		&:hover
			background: linear-gradient(180deg, #24FAED 0%, #22F6E6 22.92%, #00F0A8 100%)
			transition: all .2s
			filter: drop-shadow(4px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5))

	&_drop-shadow
	&_white
		border: 1px solid #009DFF
		background-color: #fff
		filter: drop-shadow(0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25))
		&:hover
			transition: all .2s
			filter: drop-shadow(4px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5))
/** end btns/ **/

// input
.input-theme
	width: 100%
	border: 0
	border-bottom: 1px solid #897979
	background: transparent
	padding-top: 40px
	padding-bottom: 5px
	opacity: 0.5
	font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif
	&::placeholder
		color: #0d0c0a
		font-weight: 300
	&:hover, &:focus
		outline: none
	&:focus
		opacity: 1
		&::placeholder
			font-size: 0
			opacity: 0
			transition: all .3s
// end input

.header
	background-image: url('./image/screenbg.png')
	background-size: cover
	padding-top: 25px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		padding-top: 15px
	.nav__links
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			height: auto
			align-items: normal
	&__nav
		display: flex
		justify-content: space-between
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1300px )
			padding: 0 15px
	&__title-screen
		padding-top: 70px
	.logo
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			align-items: normal
		svg
			@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
				width: 30px
				height: 30px

.title-screen
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	align-items: center
	&__btn
		margin-top: 45px
	&__advantages-list
		padding-top: 190px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			padding-top: 80px
.titles-main
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		text-align: center
	&__title
		font-size: 30px
		color: #000
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			font-size: 24px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			font-size: 18px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			font-size: 14px
		&_pos-right
			align-self: flex-end
			@media screen and ( max-width:  530px)
				align-self: auto
		&_large
			font-size: 250px
			background: linear-gradient(#00070D 3.6%, #009DFF 52%, #FFF 96%)
			-webkit-background-clip: text
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent
			color: #0B2349
			@media screen and ( max-width:  1300px)
				font-size: 160px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
				font-size: 130px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
				font-size: 93px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 520px )
				font-size: 55px
		&_margin-left
			margin-left: 200px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 520px )
				margin-left: 0
				font-weight: 700
				font-size: 18px
				text-align: center

.nav
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
		padding: 0 10px
	&__wrap-right
		display: flex
		justify-content: flex-end
		width: 100%
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			justify-content: space-between
		@media screen and ( max-width: 520px )
			justify-content: flex-end
	&__links
		height: 30px
		display: flex
		align-items: center
		
	&__link
		font-size: 12px
		color: #000
		font-weight: normal
		text-decoration: none
		margin-left: 60px
		white-space: nowrap
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			margin-left: 30px
		&_hide
			@media screen and ( max-width: 520px )
				display: none
		@media screen and ( max-width: 520px )
			margin-left: 20px
				
			
	&__btn
		margin-left: 50px
		white-space: nowrap
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			font-size: 8px
			margin-left: 20px
			max-width: 120px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 680px )
			display: none
.advantages-list
	padding-left: 0
	margin: 0
	list-style: none
	display: flex
	justify-content: center
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
		padding: 80px 10px 0
	&__list-item
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			text-align: center
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			flex: 33%
		&:not(:first-child)
			margin-left: 90px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
				margin-left: 20px
	&__text
		font-size: 20px
		font-weight: bold
		max-width: 210px
		margin-top: 30px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			font-size: 16px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 12px
			font-weight: 400


// main
.page-title
	font-size: 38px
	font-weight: 900
	color: #005387
	margin: 0
	text-align: center
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
		font-size: 34px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		font-size: 26px
.page-subtitle
	font-size: 18px
	margin: 0
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
		font-size: 16px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		font-size: 12px
// services
.services
	padding-top: 110px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		padding-top: 50px
	&__wrapper
		display: flex
		flex-direction: column
		align-items: center
	&__subtitle
		display: block
		margin-top: 25px
		max-width: 550px
		line-height: 22px
		text-align: center
		br
			@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
				display: none
	&__list-service
		display: flex
		flex-direction: row
		flex-wrap: wrap
		justify-content: space-between
		padding-top: 95px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			padding-top: 60px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			flex-direction: column
			align-items: center
			justify-content: auto
	&__btn
		margin-top: 145px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
			margin-top: 70px

.list-service
	width: 100%
.service-item
	border-radius: 26px
	position: relative
	padding-left: 25px
	padding-top: 20px
	padding-bottom: 285px
	width: 100%
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
		padding-bottom: 220px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		padding-bottom: 110px
	&__line
		margin: 0
		position: relative
		display: inline-block
	&__image
		position: absolute
		border-radius: 26px
		display: block
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
			width: 80%
	&__number
		font-size: 150px
		font-weight: 900
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
			font-size: 120px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 100px
	&__title
		font-size: 36px
		position: absolute
		top: 50%
		left: 85%
		transform: translateY(-50%)
		color: #000
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
			font-size: 26px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 20px
	&_type-1
		width: 100%
		background: linear-gradient(252.37deg, #3152C9 20.25%, #009DFF 58.29%, #6DC5FC 88.26%), rgba(205, 12, 17, 0.99)
		margin-bottom: 30px
		.service-item__image
			right: 0
			bottom: 0
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
				width: 60%
	&_type-2
		width: 60%
		background: linear-gradient(144.61deg, #8AFF80 6.82%, #175A00 80.73%), #E78A00
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1200px )
			// max-width: 510px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			// max-width: 460px	
		.service-item__image
			@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
				max-width: 500px
				bottom: 0
				right: 0
			
	&_type-3
		width: 35%
		margin-left: 30px
		background: linear-gradient(162.11deg, #2763D7 17.44%, #6AE5FE 66.53%)
		.service-item__image
			@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
				max-width: 230px
				bottom: -25%
				right: 0
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		width: 100%
		max-width: 100%
		margin: 0
	&:not(:first-child)
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			margin-top: 20px
	

		
// end services
// price
.price
	padding-top: 120px
	padding-bottom: 180px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
		padding-bottom: 100px
	&__wrapper
		display: flex
		flex-direction: column
		align-items: center
	&__content-title
		font-size: 24px
		font-weight: 700
		text-align: center
		margin-top: 0
		margin-bottom: 40px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 20px
			font-weight: 400
	&__accordion
		padding-top: 60px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			padding-top: 30px
	&__info
		padding-top: 40px
	&__price-footer
		display: flex
		justify-content: center
		width: 100%
		padding-top: 70px
	&__btn
		margin: 0 20px
		&_hide
			@media screen and ( max-width: 424px )
				display: none

.price
	.accordionItemHeading__col,
	.accordionItemContent__text
		flex: 33%
		&:not(:first-child)
			margin-left: 10px
	.accordionItemHeading__col
		@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
			display: flex
			flex-direction: column
			align-items: flex-start
	.accordionItemContent__text
		&:not(:first-child)
			@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
				text-align: center


.price-info
	max-width: 680px
	&__title
		font-size: 18px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
			font-size: 16px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 14px
	&__text
		margin: 20px 0 0
		font-size: 14px
		line-height: 16px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 12px
// accordion
.accordionWrapper
	width: 100%
	background:#fff
.accordionItem
	display: block
	width: 100%
	box-sizing: border-box

.accordionItemHeading
	position: relative
	cursor: pointer
	padding: 30px 145px 20px 80px
	background: #DFEFFC
	color: #fff
	width: 100%
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	&::before
		content: ''
		position: absolute
		right: 27px
		top: calc(50% - 21px)
		display: block
		width: 43px
		height: 43px
		border: 1px solid #000000
		border-radius: 50%
		background-image: url('./image/arrow.svg')
		background-repeat: no-repeat
		background-position: 50%
		@media screen and ( max-width: 640px )
			display: none
	&__col
		display: flex
		align-items: center
		font-size: 20px
		font-weight: 700
		color: #000000
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			font-size: 16px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			font-size: 14px
			
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 12px
			font-weight: normal
		&_maw-200
			max-width: 200px
		
.close .accordionItemContent
	height: 0px
	transition: height 1s ease-out
	transform: scaleY(0)
	display: block
    
.open .accordionItemContent
	width: 100%
	display: block
	transform: scaleY(1)
	transform-origin: top
	transition: transform 0.4s ease

.accordionItemContent
	&__col
		margin-top: 5px
		display: flex
		justify-content: space-between
		padding: 20px 145px 20px 80px
		background: rgba(248, 248, 248, 0.8)
		&:nth-child(2n)
			background: rgba(239, 239, 239, 0.85)

	&__text
		max-width: 200px
		width: 100%
		font-size: 16px
		color: #000000
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			font-size: 12px
			
.accordionItemContent__col,
.accordionItemHeading
	@media screen and ( max-width: 640px )
		padding-right: 20px
		padding-left: 20px

.open .accordionItemHeading
	margin: 0px
	border-top-left-radius: 3px
	border-top-right-radius: 3px
	border-bottom-right-radius: 0px
	border-bottom-left-radius: 0px

// equipment-price
.equipment-price
	padding-top: 80px
	.accordionItemContent__text
		max-width: 100%
		&:first-child
			width: 80%
		&:last-child
			width: 20%
			text-align: center
// end equipment-price
// mounting-price
.mounting-price
	padding-top: 70px
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	align-items: center
	.accordionItem
		margin-top: 55px
	.accordionItemHeading__col
		width: 25%
		&:not(:first-child)
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
				margin-left: 10px
	.accordionItemContent__text
		max-width: 100%
		width: 25%
	.price-info
		max-width: 630px
		&__title
			line-height: 22px
// end accordion
// end price
// examples
.examples
	padding-top: 95px
	padding-bottom: 200px
	background: linear-gradient(151.79deg, #0A2D55 10.33%, #082858 77.04%)
	@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
		padding-bottom: 100px
		padding-top: 60px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
		padding-bottom: 130px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		padding-bottom: 80px
	&__title
		color: #ffffff
		text-align: center
	&__wrapper
		padding-top: 90px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			padding-top: 50px
	.swiper-container
		width: 100%
		max-width: 1500px
		height: 440px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
			height: 240px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
			overflow: inherit
	.swiper-slide
		width: 770px
		height: 100%
		// background: #C4C4C4
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			max-width: 570px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			max-width: 470px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 560px )
			max-width: 311px
			
		img
			position: absolute
			left: 50%
			top: 50%
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
			width: 100%
			opacity: 0.2
			transition: opacity 0.5s
			border-radius: 15px
		&.swiper-slide-active
			img
				opacity: 1

	.slider-button-prev,
	.slider-button-next
		color: #4DE1FF

	.slider-button-prev
		transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(-1)
		left: 15%
		@media screen and ( max-width: 700px )
			left: calc( 50% - 58px )
	.slider-button-next
		right: 15%
		@media screen and ( max-width: 700px )
			right: calc( 50% - 58px )
			
	.slider-button-prev,
	.slider-button-next
		@media screen and ( max-width: 700px )
			top: auto
			bottom: -30% 

// end examples
// certificates
.certificates
	padding-top: 90px
	padding-bottom: 90px
	background-color: #fff
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		padding-top: 65px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		padding-bottom: 40px
	&__title
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			max-width: 200px
			margin: 0 auto
	&__wrapper
.swiper-box
	max-width: 335px
	margin: 0 auto
	padding-top: 90px
	padding-bottom: 90px
	position: relative
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		padding-top: 40px
		max-width: 300px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		max-width: 250px
	.swiper-wrapper
		box-shadow: 40px 40px 40px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)
		background-color: #C4C4C4
		background-size: cover
		background-image: url('./image/sert-bg.jpg')
	.swiper-slide
		width: 450px
		position: relative
		&__container
			width: 100%
			padding-top: 133.3333%
		img
			display: block
			width: 75%
			position: absolute
			left: 12.5%
			top: 10.5%
		&:hover
			opacity: 1

	.swiper-pagination
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			bottom: -5%
	.slider-button-next
		color: #009DFF
	.slider-button-prev
		transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(-1)
		right: 110%
		left: auto
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			left: 0
	.slider-button-next
		left: 110%
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			left: auto
			right: 0
	.slider-button-prev,
	.slider-button-next
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			top: auto
			bottom: -14%
	.swiper-pagination-bullet
		width: 16px
		height: 16px
		background-color: #C4C4C4
		opacity: 1
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			width: 12px
			height: 12px
	.swiper-pagination-bullet-active
		background: #00B7FF
.swiper-container-horizontal
	> .swiper-pagination-bullets 
		.swiper-pagination-bullet		
			margin: 0 8px
// end - certificates
// blog
.blog
	padding-top: 90px
	padding-bottom: 90px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
		padding-bottom: 60px
	&__subtitle
		text-align: center
		margin: 25px auto 50px auto
		max-width: 700px
	&__btn
		margin: 40px auto 0
	&__wrapper
		display: flex
		justify-content: center
		margin-left: -15px
		margin-right: -15px
		padding: 0 15px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
			flex-wrap: wrap
			
	&__item
		flex: 33%
		margin-left: 15px
		margin-right: 15px
		&:not(:first-child)
			@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
				margin-top: 50px
			
		&:last-child
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1023px )
				margin-top: 30px
		img
			width: 100%
			border-radius: 15px

.blog-item
	&__title
		display: block
		font-size: 22px
		font-weight: 800
		margin-top: 40px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			font-weight: 500
	&__text
		margin-top: 20px
		line-height: 17px
		font-size: 14px
	// end blog
// video-blog
.video-blog
	padding-top: 50px
	padding-bottom: 90px
	background: linear-gradient(252.37deg, #00EEFF 20.25%, #009DFF 58.29%, #6DC5FC 88.26%), rgba(205, 12, 17, 0.99)
	@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
		padding-top: 20px
	@media screen and ( max-width: 767px )
		padding-bottom: 40px
	&__title
		color: #fff
	&__wrapper
		text-align: center
		max-width: 1120px
		margin: 0 auto
		@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )
			max-width: 800px
		@media screen and ( max-width: 768px )
		@media screen and ( max-width: 530px )
			max-width: 300px
		iframe
			width: 100%
			height: 630px
			@media screen and ( max-width: 1024px )

// contacts
.contacts
	padding-top: 70px
	padding-bottom: 165px
	background-image: url('./image/mapbg.jpg')
	background-size: cover
	&__title
		font-size: 38px
		font-weight: 900
	&__card
		margin-top: 70px
.card-contact
	background-color: #ffffff
	max-width: 390px
	width: 100%
	padding: 50px 40px 70px 75px
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	&__locate
		position: relative
		font-size: 20px
		font-weight: 800
		display: block
		&::before
			content: ''
			position: absolute
			display: block
			left: -30px
			top: 50%
			transform: translateY(-50%)
			width: 14px
			height: 17px
			background-image: url('./image/marker.svg')

	&__item
		font-size: 14px
		color: #232323
		text-decoration: none
		margin-top: 10px
		&_lh26
			line-height: 26px
		&_link
			transition: all .2s
			text-decoration: underline
			text-decoration-color: transparent
			&:hover
				text-decoration-color: #232323
				transition: all .2s
